00042 std::string process_itaps_error( int ierr )
00043 {
00044   std::string result( "ITAPS ERROR: " );
00045   switch (ierr) {
00046     case iBase_MESH_ALREADY_LOADED:      result += "File Already Loaded";   break;
00047     case iBase_FILE_NOT_FOUND:           result += "File Not Found";        break;
00048     case iBase_FILE_WRITE_ERROR:         result += "File Write Error";      break;
00049     case iBase_NIL_ARRAY:                result += "NULL Array";            break;
00050     case iBase_BAD_ARRAY_SIZE:           result += "Bad Array Size";        break;
00051     case iBase_BAD_ARRAY_DIMENSION:      result += "Bad Array Dimension";   break;
00052     case iBase_INVALID_ENTITY_HANDLE:    result += "Invalid Handle";        break;
00053     case iBase_INVALID_ENTITY_COUNT:     result += "Invalid Count";         break;
00054     case iBase_INVALID_ENTITY_TYPE:      result += "Invalid Type";          break;
00055     case iBase_INVALID_ENTITY_TOPOLOGY:  result += "Invalid Topology";      break;
00056     case iBase_BAD_TYPE_AND_TOPO:        result += "Invalid Type";          break;
00057     case iBase_ENTITY_CREATION_ERROR:    result += "Creation Failed";       break;
00058     case iBase_INVALID_TAG_HANDLE:       result += "Invalid Tag";           break;
00059     case iBase_TAG_NOT_FOUND:            result += "Tag Not Found";         break;
00060     case iBase_TAG_ALREADY_EXISTS:       result += "Tag Exists";            break;
00061     case iBase_TAG_IN_USE:               result += "Tag In Use";            break;
00062     case iBase_INVALID_ENTITYSET_HANDLE: result += "Invalid Handle";        break;
00063     case iBase_INVALID_ITERATOR_HANDLE:  result += "Invalid Iterator";      break;
00064     case iBase_INVALID_ARGUMENT:         result += "Invalid Argument";      break;
00065     case iBase_MEMORY_ALLOCATION_FAILED: result += "Out of Memory";         break;
00066     case iBase_NOT_SUPPORTED:            result += "Not Supported";         break;
00067     default:                             result += "Uknown/Internal Error"; break;
00068   }
00069   MSQ_DBGOUT(1) << result << std::endl;
00070   return result;
00071 }
